<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>10702</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>20203</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利的嗅觉比大多数人都好，但他没有一个真正的森林鼻子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>20203</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>26202</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>所以，他花了更长的时间才能找到气味。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>26202</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>29922</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是布尔迪奥！”他低声说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>29922</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>32501</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他一定在跟踪我的脚印。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>32501</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>36753</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我能看到他的枪在阳光下闪闪发光。看！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>36753</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>40752</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一些灌木丛中飞快地闪过一道亮光。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>40752</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>43252</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是，他们都看到了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>43252</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>47752</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>四只年轻的狼突然向山坡下跑去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>47752</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>51501</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们要去哪里？”毛克利说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>51501</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>56753</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“打猎！”格瑞布拉德回答说，“跟我们走！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>56753</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>61502</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我不可以。人类不猎杀其他人类！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>61502</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>64002</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利在他们后面喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>64002</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>68180</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>阿克拉看了他一眼，毛克利躲开了目光。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>68180</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>74502</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们就找到这个人，看看他想要做什么吧。”巴希拉说道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>74502</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>82502</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利向前跑，无声地穿过森林，跟在年轻的狼后面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>82502</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>86002</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大家跟在后面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>86002</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>91116</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>果然不出所料，当毛克利拨开一些灌木丛时，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>91116</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>93518</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他看见了布尔迪奥。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>93518</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>98018</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>布尔迪奥肩上背着枪，沿路走过来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>98018</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>102767</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，他停了下来，困惑地看着地面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>102767</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>107767</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>阿克拉在毛克利旁边轻轻地笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>107767</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>115518</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“今天早上，我在山路上加了些脚印，脚印通往不同的方向。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>115518</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>121517</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“难怪布尔迪奥糊涂了。”毛克利笑着轻声说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>121517</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>125360</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>最后，猎人叹了一口气，坐下了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>125360</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>130037</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他不知道毛克利和动物们就在附近看着他。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>130037</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>132785</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他愤怒地自言自语。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>132785</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>136786</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他在说什么？”巴希拉问毛克利。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>136786</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>140534</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他很快翻译出布尔迪奥的话。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>140534</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>145036</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他说‘狼群一定在我周围跳舞了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>145036</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>148285</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我从没见过这样的山路！’</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>148285</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>153115</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>现在，他在抱怨自己又累又饿。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>153115</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>155951</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>布尔迪奥吃了一些坚果。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>155951</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>159952</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>不一会儿，几个男人沿路走了过来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>159952</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>163202</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们也坐下休息。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>163202</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>167952</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>布尔迪奥开始给他们讲一些荒唐的故事。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>167952</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>171703</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利听的时候，差点笑出声来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>171703</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>176953</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>布尔迪奥告诉那些人，是他杀死了大老虎谢尔坎。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>176953</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>181452</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，他说一个男孩儿把自己变成了狼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>181452</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>184601</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我和他打了一下午。”猎人说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>184601</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>188968</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我觉得他在我的枪上施了巫术。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>188968</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>192969</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你为什么这么说？”其中一个男人问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>192969</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>199468</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“一颗对准他的子弹突然旋转，打中了我自己的一头水牛！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>199468</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>201718</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我是最棒的猎手。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>201718</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>204718</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>所以，我的村庄派我来抓他。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>204718</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>209348</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利的朋友们担心地看了他一眼。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>209348</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>212667</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然而，毛克利仍然咧嘴笑着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>212667</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>218669</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他的故事很荒唐。但是，那些男人相信他！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>218669</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>223206</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“同时，村民们把麦苏雅和她的丈夫关了起来。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>223206</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>227269</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>布尔迪奥说，“他们也是巫师。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>227269</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>233518</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>事实上，他们是最坏的一类，因为他们在抚养那个狼孩儿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>233518</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>238018</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们将受到惩罚，甚至可能被烧死。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>238018</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>241268</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>男人们大吃一惊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>241268</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>244268</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“什么时候？”有人问道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>244268</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>249147</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“在我带着那个男孩儿的尸体回去之前，什么也不会发生的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>249147</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>253918</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>布尔迪奥回答道，“对了，我觉得他就在附近。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>253918</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>255670</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>你们见过他吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>255670</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>259418</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>巴希拉又看了一眼毛克利。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>259418</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>263167</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他注意到那个男孩儿的表情变了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>263167</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>267407</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“男人们在说什么？”黑豹低声说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>267407</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>270984</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利表情沉重地翻译着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>270984</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>276740</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他解释说村民们把麦苏雅和她的丈夫关了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>276740</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>282486</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“什么？”格瑞布拉德困惑地摇了摇头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>282486</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>285484</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“人类互相猎杀？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>285484</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>290484</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“布尔迪奥这么说的。”毛克利皱着眉头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>290484</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>295485</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他的话我不能完全听懂，人类都疯了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>295485</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>301768</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但我知道一点：麦苏雅和她丈夫没有做错什么。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>301768</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>305891</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们只是给我饭吃，给我地方住而已。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>305891</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>310385</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>毛克利又听了一些布尔迪奥说的话。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>69</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>310385</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>314135</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他的表情越来越坚定。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>70</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>314135</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>316885</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我要回到村庄去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>71</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>316885</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>320636</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我不会让他们杀了麦苏雅！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>